WEBVTT

00:01.379 --> 00:04.070
I cannot believe that you
are actually a minister.

00:04.196 --> 00:05.881
[Ethereal music plays]

00:06.047 --> 00:07.324
Yes, my lamb.

00:07.449 --> 00:09.527
I can marry people, bury people,

00:09.652 --> 00:10.861
grant wishes.

00:10.986 --> 00:13.138
- Honey, you're not a genie.
- Oh.

00:13.304 --> 00:15.266
You know, I am so honored
that Amanda asked me

00:15.391 --> 00:16.767
to officiate her wedding.

00:16.892 --> 00:20.479
And I need to honor her
with the perfect outfit.

00:20.645 --> 00:21.772
Next minister outfit, please.

00:21.938 --> 00:24.399
Both: Ooh.

00:24.565 --> 00:25.484
I like it.

00:25.867 --> 00:28.028
You don't think
it's just a little breasty?

00:28.194 --> 00:31.156
- Yes, totally breasty.
- Yeah.

00:31.322 --> 00:34.159
- Oh, you mean in a bad way.
- Mm-hmm.

00:34.325 --> 00:35.577
Thank you.

00:35.743 --> 00:37.663
You're gonna have so much fun.

00:37.829 --> 00:39.456
Man, I'd give anything to go.

00:39.622 --> 00:40.958
But being on a plane
for five hours with Amy,

00:41.083 --> 00:42.417
no thank you.

00:42.583 --> 00:44.528
Don't they make, like, a
little carrier thing for babies

00:44.653 --> 00:46.197
like they do for pomeranians?

00:46.322 --> 00:48.215
That way you could just stow her.

00:48.381 --> 00:50.676
I'm gonna let you answer that
question for yourself, honey.

00:50.842 --> 00:53.437
But seriously, though,
being stuck on a flight

00:53.562 --> 00:55.639
with a baby who's melting down,

00:55.805 --> 00:57.575
ugh, I hate to say this,

00:57.700 --> 00:59.685
but I hate those people.

00:59.851 --> 01:02.263
I have called the cops
on those people.

01:02.388 --> 01:03.597
No, it'll be great.

01:03.722 --> 01:05.966
It'll just be me and Kevin,
which will be fun.

01:06.091 --> 01:07.151
Although...

01:07.276 --> 01:09.653
Bringing a boyfriend
to a wedding is fraught.

01:09.819 --> 01:12.323
It's nonstop, "when are you
getting married?"

01:12.448 --> 01:14.116
"When are you
gonna pop the question?"

01:14.282 --> 01:17.394
I'm like, "get the hell out
of my face, mee-maw."

01:17.519 --> 01:19.196
And it's even worse for me,

01:19.321 --> 01:22.766
even though I have absolutely
no desire to get married.

01:22.891 --> 01:25.002
Not for me.

01:25.168 --> 01:26.128
Not even with Kevin?

01:26.294 --> 01:27.438
No, I love Kevin.

01:27.563 --> 01:30.382
But I am a strong single lady.

01:30.548 --> 01:32.993
I'm Ava, I don't even
need a last name.

01:33.118 --> 01:35.137
I certainly don't need his.

01:35.303 --> 01:37.180
Ugh, it's gonna be
a challenging weekend.

01:37.346 --> 01:40.217
God, give me strength.

01:40.342 --> 01:43.187
Ooh, I think he heard me.

01:43.312 --> 01:46.982
I felt him reach down and touch
me with his E.T. finger.

01:47.148 --> 01:48.692
Both: Ooh.

01:48.817 --> 01:51.153
Let's see a spin.

01:51.319 --> 01:53.321
Oh, no!

01:53.487 --> 01:55.032
N-o on the coin slot.

